          <div className="info-item">
            <span>üí° This uses the real 1inch API</span>
          </div>
          <div className="info-item">
            <span>üîê Your wallet stays secure</span>
          </div>
          <div className="info-item">
            <span>‚ö° Best rates from 139 protocols</span>
